snippet.title: Minecraft: Story Mode Episode 6 - 'A Portal to Mystery' Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Continuing their journey through the portal hallway, Jesse and crew land themselves in another strange new world - one completely overrun by zombies. With a timely invitation to take refuge in a spooky mansion, they find themselves thrown into a thrilling mystery alongside famous members of the Minecraft community: Stampy Cat, Stacy Plays, DanTDM (The Diamond Minecart), LDShadowLady, AND CaptainSparklez!
